>Description:
In most OS X applications in which you work with a specific file an icon is displayed net to the file name. Dragging this icon to e.g. the terminal will paste the file path. To see an example, open a file in Preview and drag the icon to a terminal. It would be nice if DrRacket also displayed such an icon.
